Washington gets more Oregonians moving in than from any other state.<br />
Those retirees are no drain on the state services, they spend a lot of money &#8211; and none of it goes to Oregon &#8211; except the shopkeepers get some when they come over the border to buy things without sales tax.<br />
Oregon is foolish to continue policies that cause this flight, but, as you say, it is what the people want&#8230;.</p>
